prompt: Cai Xukun, a young Chinese pop idol, stands at the entrance of a bustling city park. He's dressed in stylish streetwear, looking slightly out of place and confused.
Donald Trump, in his signature suit and red tie, strides confidently across the park's main path, his expression a mix of determination and bewilderment.
A friendly golden retriever trots between Cai Xukun and Donald Trump, its tail wagging as it looks up at them expectantly.
A solitary bicycle wheel leans against a park bench, its presence oddly conspicuous in the middle of the greenery.
Cai Xukun cautiously approaches the dog, extending a hand for it to sniff. His face shows a mixture of curiosity and gentle apprehension.
Trump gesticulates wildly, pointing at the wheel and then at the sky, as if trying to explain a complex theory to his unlikely companions.
The golden retriever sits obediently, looking back and forth between Cai Xukun and Trump, its head tilted in apparent confusion at their interaction.
The bicycle wheel begins to wobble, then rolls slowly across the park path, guided by an unseen force.
Cai Xukun's eyes widen in surprise as he watches the wheel's movement. He takes a few tentative steps to follow it.
Trump's face lights up with a triumphant grin. He marches after the rolling wheel, beckoning Cai Xukun and the dog to follow him on this bizarre adventure.
